high_descs: Move to the smaller desk with a lamp on it, to your right.
Pick up the red credit card on the desk.
Bring the credit card to the larger desk on the right.
Put the card in the gray bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl with card on the desk.
Bring the bowl with card to the smaller desk on the left.
Put the bowl with card on the desk, left of the CD.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a credit card in it on the small desk.

high_descs: Turn around and move forward, then turn left to go to the desk with the lamp on it.
Pick up the credit card from the desk.
Turn around and step forward, then turn left and go toward the book case, then turn left to face the desk.
Put the credit card in the bowl on the desk.
Pick up the bowl from the desk.
Return to the desk with the lamp, to your left.
Place the bowl on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a credit card in it on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to face the card on the desk.
Pick up the card on the desk.
Take a step to the right to face the computer desk.
Place the card in the bowl on the computer desk.
Pick up the bowl on the computer desk.
Step to the left to face the desk.
Place the bowl on the desk.
anns.task_desc: To put a card in a bowl plus move them to the left desk.
